  "text": "obtained from finite difference discretizations of one dimensional nonlinear wave equations. For ease of presentation we first illustrate by an example our approach of deriving large sparse Hamiltonian systems from Hamiltonian PDEs. For further examples we refer to [CITATION_1] .",
